{"prompt": "Generate a website for a smart home technology. The website should be user-friendly and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Smart Home Innovations</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #2196F3;\n            --secondary-blue: #42A5F5;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --footer-color: #f5f5f5;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-blue) 0%, var(--secondary-blue) 100%);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: white;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--footer-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Smart Home Innovations</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#features\">Features</a>\n                <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Welcome to Your Smarter Home</h2>\n            <p>Experience the future of living with our cutting-edge smart home technology. Control your lights, security, climate, and more with effortless ease.</p>\n            <a href=\"#features\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Solutions</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"features\" id=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Key Features</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                    <h3>Smart Lighting</h3>\n                    <p>Automate your lighting, set moods, and save energy with intelligent control.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                    <h3>Home Security</h3>\n                    <p>Monitor your home from anywhere with smart cameras, sensors, and alarm systems.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-thermometer-half\"></i>\n                    <h3>Climate Control</h3>\n                    <p>Optimize your home's temperature for comfort and efficiency with smart thermostats.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                